{"tid":1390823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中美第12輪貿易談判破裂     美國官員提早結束離開上海","createTime":"2019-07-31T08:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T08:56:07.000Z","uid":35790,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a7a53dc2219ccec1513004707cbead252e4b9d","tid":1390823,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:48:32.000Z","msg":"中美第12輪貿易談判破裂 提早結束離開上海<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-31<br />\n<br />\n第十二輪中美貿易磋商在上海提前結束。根據彭博社等報導，中美貿易團隊於下午1時37分左右在上海拍照留念並握手。美國官員沒有發表任何公開言論，立即驅車前往機場，離開上海。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，根據之前的時間表，攝影中美最初安排在下午2時15分左右才結束。暫時未有任何一位官員發表公開言論。美國官員隨後立即啟程前往機場。<br />\n<br />\n中美代表今早在上海舉行第二日高級別貿易磋商。大陸副總理劉鶴與美國貿易代表賴海哲(Robert Lighthizer)，以及財長米努勤(Steven Mnuchin)會前先握手和合照，雙方再開始正式會談。<br />\n<br />\n外界早前預期，雙方不會作出重大原則性讓步，預計此次貿易磋商不會取得重大突破。<br />\n&lt;聯合&gt;"},{"pid":"c49a8943b4bfa8cc66a3f512eebf8f5efd1a775d","tid":1390823,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:48:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VfuWZd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuWZd5.png&h=4576ca37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cSQ2oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cSQ2oL.png&h=cef8ee5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkT1vED.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkT1vED.png&h=0accd33f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"eb442a7091f1122b3db384389a74ed27754d8de5","tid":1390823,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</